div.div:
Lee Han, a Graduate student, was reborn as the youngest son in another worlds famous family of mages.
He swore he would never go to another place with the word academy in it. However, the magic academy known as Einrogard completely ignored what he had promised himself.
Being independent is a must; monsters may appear, and the professors are all nutjobs! The beginning of a pathetic academy life that you have never seen before.
Life as a magic academy mage, Will I be able to graduate safely?

Its a world where a magical tree grows from the back of a swordsman, a mute girl is turned into a living weapon by her mother, a frost dragon roams the skies seeking vengeance, and beings with godlike powers clash for the balance of nature. In the middle of it all is Bira, an orphaned boy, happily spending his days fishing inside a secluded forest. Then he meets Tanyu, a former general on a quest to find his childhood love. Together, they journey into an enchanted landscape unlike any other. (Source: Tapas)
